summary:
I have an extensive experience in the production, demand and supply planning. I have the capability to work in fast paced dynamic environment, have the ability to show initiative and have a Pro-active approach. I have the ability to build good relationships, to communicate bad news as well as good to all levels of the business and have the strength of character to deal with tight situations and difficult customers.

Specialties: Warehouse management, 
Supply chain management, 
Experience of working within a matrix / European structure Able to maintain direction without direct supervision
